      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it sounds kinda complicated. u mentioned potential job losses in coal, but also jobs in solar. is it pretty much a given that the solar jobs will replace what's lost in coal, or is that just a hope? i've heard some people saying that the move away from coal is just something that has to happen anyway because of the climate, so i'm wondering if the \"cons\" are actually even a big deal in the long run?",
